This week, I had the privilege of attending the State of the Union as Congressman Trey Hollingsworth’s guest. 

Watching the SOTU in our nation’s Capital was a unique experience, & I thank Congressman Hollingsworth for this opportunity & his leadership in our community. https://t.co/QtKfhQt8EQ

Just spoke with @RepTrey Hollingsworth (R-IN9) on the impeachment vote- he says he voted against b/c in his words "the sham political resolution.. still yet doesn't provide the President with due process."

More tonight & Sunday on this week's edition of @INFocusIndiana

full_text: I voted against today’s Democrat resolution to deprive @POTUS of his due process and against continuing a partisan investigation. House Democrats have misappropriated a solemn constitutional duty to delegitimize an election and the 62 million voters who supported our President.
